                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>me a great loss. If, therefore, you<lb/> can help me out, send me\n                                        whatever<lb/> you can spare, only if they are<lb/> Kosher,\n                                        even though not so handsome.<lb/> You will be doing me a\n                                        great service.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Ready to serve you at any<lb/> time.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Yours, in distress, and<lb/> wishing you a happy\n                                        New Year.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\"><persName role=\"author\">N.\n                                        Ottinger</persName>.</p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
