                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>\n                                        <add>\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">Yiddish</hi>\n                                        </add>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                                        <placeName>N Y</placeName>\n                                        <date>13<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> of Sept. 1850</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>He who grants life to all living may he grant<lb/> all that is good\n                                        to my friend, <persName>Rabbi Isaac</persName>.<lb/> I\n                                        received your letter and note that<lb/> you are again\n                                        sending me prayer books<lb/> and pentateuchs, but I have\n                                        not<lb/> yet received them. I cannot wait,<lb/> and send you\n                                        eight dollars as<lb/> you request. If you have not yet<lb/>\n                                        sent out the goods, send it to me as<lb/> soon as possible.\n                                        I want to ask<lb/> you to send me several <add>?</add>,<lb/>\n                                        for I am in great difficulty. The<lb/> box of <add>?</add>\n                                        which I ordered Â½<lb/> year ago have been taken by\n                                                  <persName>Mr.<lb/> Karschet</persName> and I\n                                        cannot provide<lb/> for <del>the</del>\n                                        <placeName>NY</placeName> communities which is to</p>"
                  },
